profile:
Welcome to Closets By Design Niagara, where we specialize in custom closets and home office. Closets By Design - Niagara can design an attractive storage space for any area of your home that needs organizing, from the pantry to the garage and everywhere in between.

At Closets by Design, we offer three closet systems to choose from. Each will maximize your space and create a closet that helps organize not only your clothes, but your life as well. We build each closet with you in mind.
